snippet.title: Nintendo Switch, Steam 「Sixtar Gate: STARTRAIL」 Teaser Movie
snippet.description:
Get ready to travel the vast cosmos in 「Sixtar Gate」
the rhythm action game for Nintendo Switch & Steam!

Let's visit various planets with Shii, your cute and lovely space navigation partner!
Sail on diverse soundtracks, and unravel stories hidden behind the planets!

Available 2021 for Nintendo Switch & Steam!

● Sixtar Gate: STARTRAIL Official Website
https://www.cfk.kr/sixtargate/
